From @euhmeuh initial version.
Print text using flowers for slack.





Works with words such as :
cool
ok
fork
code

Or any words containing letters :
c, e, d, f, i, h, k, l, o, r, u





Usage: flowers.py [-h] [--spaced] t

Print some flowers.

positional arguments:
  t           The text to print, letters must be within : a, c, e, d, f, i, h,
              k, l, o, s, r, u, t, <space>

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  --spaced    Spaces between letters (default: False)

